snippet.title: Prototype 2 (PC Gameplay)
snippet.description:
FSG Presents: Prototype 2 PC

Sequel to Radical Entertainment's 2009 open-world action game, Prototype 2 for the PC is terribly awesome. 

Check out Prototype 2:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/115320/
